            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>The National Bureau of Investigation (NBI) is the premier investigative agency of the Philippines, established to provide high-quality investigative and intelligence services to the nation. As a crucial component of the Department of Justice, we are committed to upholding the rule of law, ensuring justice, and maintaining national security through professional investigation and law enforcement.</p>
